definitions.definition: To dance by intentionally jumping into and colliding with other, similarly behaving dancers, and performing other wild , aggressive , or spastic movements .
To intentionally jump into and collide with (another dancer) at a concert.

main_definition: ( intransitive ) To dance by intentionally jumping into and colliding with other, similarly behaving dancers, and performing other wild , aggressive , or spastic movements .
secondary_definitions: ( transitive , rare ) To intentionally jump into and collide with (another dancer) at a concert.
